metadata.name: Rabbit's View
metadata.description:
Rabbit's view represents London from the perspective of Alice's rabbit and from the artist Sara Alarcón when she traveled to this city, in the artwork the main symbols of the city are distorted by the color and the movement.  
The purchase of the NFT comes with the original physical artwork in acrylic and pastel on canvas 50x50cm.  
Only for the first buyer.
metadata.Physical artwork: Hi! Thanks you for supporting my art, if you are the first buyer please email me to: sara.alarcon.arango@gmail.com your info to send you the physical artwork.
